{"tid":610680,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中海油今年產量目標4.7-4.8億桶油當量","createTime":"2018-03-30T07:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T07:32:35.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"879143cc4ffcf73d4d324cf842526b0fb4e25208","tid":610680,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"香港電台-財經<br />\n中海油去年資本開支497.2億元人民幣，按年反彈2%。<br />\n集團指，今年資本開支目標進一步升至700-800億元，產量目標亦升至4.7-4.8億桶油當量，年內將有5個新項目投產。<br />\n<br />\n去年淨產量約4.7億桶油當量，按年跌1.4%，但仍超額完成目標。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/中海油今年產量目標4-7-4-8億桶油當量-103205985.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ffinance%2F%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E6%B2%B9%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%94%A2%E9%87%8F%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%994-7-4-8%E5%84%84%E6%A1%B6%E6%B2%B9%E7%95%B6%E9%87%8F-103205985.html&d=yY4n0Etsvt53l5azvnt8ZttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=30ecd0c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/中海油今年產量目標4-7-4-8億桶油當量-103205985.html</a>"}]}